{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/learn-scss/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Learn SCSS in 5 minutes</p>\n<p>SCSS simply means Sassy CSS.</p>\n<p>Sassy CSS is a CSS preprocessor that gives you access to use features that are not available in Vanilla CSS</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"variables\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#variables\" aria-label=\"variables permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Variables</h2>\n<p>To create a variable just add a $sign to the variable name and set them like a normal CSS property.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">$product-dark-blue: #324e85\n$product-light-blue: #4c7396\n$product-lighter-blue: #9bb7cf\n\n.element</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> $product-dark-blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"nesting\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#nesting\" aria-label=\"nesting permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Nesting</h2>\n<p>SCSS helps you write cleaner and concise CSS.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.container</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> gray<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> green<span class=\"token selector\">;\n\n  div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid black<span class=\"token selector\">;\n    a</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">text-decoration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #f2f2f2<span class=\"token selector\">;\n      &amp;::hover</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #d2d2d2<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"inheritance\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#inheritance\" aria-label=\"inheritance permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Inheritance</h2>\n<p>@extends help you inherit the properties of another class.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.header</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> gray<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.sub-header</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@extend</span> .header<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 40px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"mixin\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#mixin\" aria-label=\"mixin permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Mixin</h2>\n<p>Mixin is another way SCSS implement inheritance using @mixin.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@mixin</span> red-color</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> gray<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.header</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@include</span> red-color<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* add mixin */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"operators\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#operators\" aria-label=\"operators permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Operators</h2>\n<p>SCSS offers you different kind of operators that you can use in your CSS.\nArithmetic operators like +, -, *, / etc</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@mixin</span> top-margin <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>$margin<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin-top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30px + $margin<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.container</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 800px - 80px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@include</span> <span class=\"token function\">top-margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"color-functions\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#color-functions\" aria-label=\"color functions permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Color functions</h2>\n<p>scss provides some function that can be used to manipulate colors.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token function\">mix</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> gray<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 30%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 30% blue, 70% gray */</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">lighten</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>#ff0000<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 30%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* #ff9999 */</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">darken</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>#ff0000<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 30%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">/* #660000 */</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>#036<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0.3<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">/* rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.79) */</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">trnasparentize</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>$color<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> $amout<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"loops\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#loops\" aria-label=\"loops permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Loops</h2>\n<p>create utility classes for your color, font-size and a lot of other properties</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@for</span> $x from 1 through 70</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">.font-size-#</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>$x<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0px + $x<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"conditions\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#conditions\" aria-label=\"conditions permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Conditions</h2>\n<p>Another awesome feature of scss is the ability to use If/else statements in css.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\">$<span class=\"token property\">bg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> pink<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n$<span class=\"token property\">bg-mobile</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token selector\">;\n\np</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@if</span> $bg == pink</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@else</span> if $bg-mobile == red</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> green<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@else</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> gray<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"documentation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#documentation\" aria-label=\"documentation permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Documentation</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://sass-lang.com/documentation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://sass-lang.com/documentation</a></p>","excerpt":"Learn SCSS in 5 minutes SCSS simply means Sassy CSS. Sassy CSS is a CSS preprocessor that gives you access to use features that are not…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/learn-scss/#variables\">Variables</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/learn-scss/#nesting\">Nesting</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/learn-scss/#inheritance\">Inheritance</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/learn-scss/#mixin\">Mixin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/learn-scss/#operators\">Operators</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/learn-scss/#color-functions\">Color functions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/learn-scss/#loops\">Loops</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/learn-scss/#conditions\">Conditions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/learn-scss/#documentation\">Documentation</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/learn-scss/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"Dec 27, 2020","title":"✒️ Learn SCSS","tags":["SCSS","CSS","learnCSS","story"],"keywords":"story, gatsby, blog, html, css, scss, learn","update":"Dec 27, 2020","read":"5m"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/learn-scss/","series":[],"lastmod":"2020-12-27"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864","63159454"]}